{"id": 2019, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对中年有哪些恐惧的想象？", "description": "脱发、养娃、情感危机…地狱的模样大概就是中年生活了吧！（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 3371, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171117130510H4LObjXVxcva5G3o.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-22T03:00:02Z", "options": [{"id": 251392, "content": "怀旧心结", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197324}, {"id": 251905, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174178}, {"id": 250371, "content": "正皮的孩子和无趣的婚姻", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142114}, {"id": 250372, "content": "记忆力衰退", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189530}, {"id": 250373, "content": "我的孩啊～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918405}, {"id": 252421, "content": "油腻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202450}, {"id": 250374, "content": "工作压力 \n不想养小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697887}, {"id": 250886, "content": "繁忙又千篇一律的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192691}, {"id": 250375, "content": "生活的巨大开销", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184180}, {"id": 250376, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597563}, {"id": 250377, "content": "不知道，我准备在步入中年之前死掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1187081}, {"id": 250633, "content": "脱发\n维持家庭\n庸庸碌碌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 254729, "content": "没有可玩的了，对任何事情失去兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086674}, {"id": 250378, "content": "无能为力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188524}, {"id": 250634, "content": "脱发\n维持家庭\n庸庸碌碌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 250379, "content": "上有老下有小烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999188}, {"id": 250380, "content": "小小的期待、偶尔的兴奋和沉默的失望……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190585}, {"id": 251148, "content": "越来越不喜欢现在的自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600361}, {"id": 251660, "content": "哇 发胖了 年轻时没来得及穿的衣服再也穿不上l", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198394}, {"id": 250381, "content": "变丑，发福", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172440}, {"id": 252429, "content": "对社会仍懵懂无知", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190360}, {"id": 250382, "content": "为生活忙碌，再也没有那无忧无虑的时光了；事业没有成就，还是普通人一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189199}, {"id": 251918, "content": "单身 没猫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190636}, {"id": 250383, "content": "生活压力越来越大，赚的钱不够花，还要养家糊口", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190747}, {"id": 250384, "content": "好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190750}, {"id": 250385, "content": "有了追求梦想的条件\n失去追求梦想的勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190754}, {"id": 250641, "content": "还在租房子住，和别人共用厕所，还得经常搬家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138453}, {"id": 250386, "content": "修仙修到活不到中年", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978842}, {"id": 250387, "content": "没房独身性冷淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190760}, {"id": 250388, "content": "穿棉裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190762}, {"id": 250390, "content": "皮肤松弛，性欲减退，脂肪堆积", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164463}, {"id": 250391, "content": "害怕整天被柴米油盐包围害怕沦为丈夫和孩子的奴隶害怕所过的生活不及早年父母提供的优越生活，这些都是我绝不允许发生的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190769}, {"id": 251927, "content": "平淡如水的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140014}, {"id": 250392, "content": "生活就是苟且，就是柴米油盐，已经看不到远方，没闲情逸致读诗了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086814}, {"id": 250393, "content": "做了不喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910931}, {"id": 250394, "content": "不想聊这么沉重的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784804}, {"id": 250650, "content": "到了要承担的年纪还没有足够的力量", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683903}, {"id": 252442, "content": "没有变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202749}, {"id": 250397, "content": "子欲养而亲不待", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190594}, {"id": 250398, "content": "记忆力下降，精力不足", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190854}, {"id": 250399, "content": "变成了自己讨厌的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190861}, {"id": 250655, "content": "就像《北京青年》中的何东一样，中年生活让他产生了“重走一回青春”的“疯狂”举动（至少在女友和家人看来是疯狂的）。他说了一句话让我觉得细思极恐，就是“我们结婚以后，担心的就是些婆婆妈妈的生活琐事”！中年生活，我有点怂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174271}, {"id": 251679, "content": "没车没房没存款。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198375}, {"id": 250400, "content": "失去了青春年少时的心境与乐趣吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720017}, {"id": 250401, "content": "没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1168874}, {"id": 251938, "content": "生活压力和个人能力、物质欲望的不匹配！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809267}, {"id": 250403, "content": "未来失去了多种可能性", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1127990}, {"id": 250404, "content": "没有生活 只有活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512634}, {"id": 250405, "content": "要不要二胎?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190875}, {"id": 250406, "content": "皱纹，没有自己的时间，失去激情，没有冲动，随遇而安", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949236}]}